Package: cdmAmsIIIaj
Title: Implementation of CDM Small-Scale Methodology AMS-III.AJ
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tidyverse-aligned tooling for the Clean Development Mechanism
    small-scale methodology AMS-III.AJ "Recovery and recycling of materials from solid wastes".
    Functions translate key equations, applicability conditions, simulation utilities,
    and workflow orchestration helpers into reproducible R code for recycling programmes.
